-- 13-progressive-summarization-frames.cell (v0.2)
-- Execution trace of 13-progressive-summarization.cell via eval-one
--
-- v0.2 execution notes:
--   - File-scope вҠЁ? active: retry max 3 with failure context, then error-value(вҠҘ)
--   - compress-further has local вҠЁ? (overrides file-scope): retry max 2 with lost-concepts
--   - compress-further uses guard clause: given acceptable where acceptable = true
--   - Guard-induced вҠҘ: when check-fidelityвҶ’acceptable = false, guard blocks
--     compress-further вҶ’ all its yields become вҠҘ вҶ’ blocks вҠўвҠў recurse-compression
--   - report uses given? to accept вҠҘ from compress-further (v0.2 optional given)
--   - вҠҘ propagation is the natural termination mechanism for the compression loop
--
-- Meta: Cell summarizes its own specification, compressing until information loss
--   is unacceptable, then halts via guard-induced вҠҘ.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
