вҠў document
  yield text, word-count

  вҠў= text вҶҗ "Cell Language Specification v0.1

What Cell Is: Cell is a self-bootstrapping metacircular language for LLMs. Programs are documents. Execution fills in values. The document IS the program IS the state. Cells start as natural language (soft) and progressively crystallize into deterministic code (hard) under oracle pressure.

Core Syntax: вҠў declares a cell with given inputs, yield outputs, вҲҙ for natural language body, вҠў= for deterministic body, вҠЁ for oracle assertions, вҠЁ? for recovery policy, В§ for quotation, В«В» for interpolation, вүЎ for binding, вҶ’ for output access, в–ё for stage annotation, вҠўвҲҳ for evolution loops.

Execution Model (eval-one): Kahn's algorithm, one step at a time. Find cells with all given inputs bound. Pick one. Evaluate it. Spawn oracle claim cells. If claims pass, freeze output. If claims fail, retry or produce вҠҘ. Properties: document-is-state, monotonicity, non-termination by design, confluence, content addressing, fusion of classical and semantic substrates.

Quotation: В§ passes a cell's definition as data. В§greet is the definition, greetвҶ’message is the output. Enables code-as-data, reflection, self-modification.

Crystallization: Progression from soft (вҲҙ) to hard (вҠў=). Verification crystallizes before computation. Oracles on soft cells are guardrails; on crystallized cells, contracts. crystallize and eval-one are permanently soft.

Oracle System: Every вҠЁ is syntactic sugar for a claim cell spawned by cell-zero. Oracle types: deterministic, structural, semantic, ambiguous. вҠЁ? defines retry with feedback. Retry is graph rewrite preserving immutability. Oracle promotion: when oracle states the implementation, runtime can crystallize.

Proof-Carrying Computation: LLM finds solution (NP space), crystallized verifier checks it (P space). Verifier always catches wrong answers.

Evolution Loops (вҠўвҲҳ): First-class fixed-point combinator over cell definitions. Interface freeze constraint: implementation changes, interface cannot. Generalizes to tournament, beam search, adversarial co-evolution.

Self-Crystallization: crystallize cell reads В§target, writes вҠў= replacement, verify-crystal checks against oracles. 'May replace' is permission (deontic). The вҲҙ is the specification, вҠў= is the optimization. Both coexist.

Bootstrap Sequence: External syntax вҶ’ LLM executes first cells вҶ’ describe parses syntax вҶ’ crystallize writes вҠў= вҶ’ verify checks вҶ’ more crystallize вҶ’ LLM cost drops. Trajectory: soft everywhere вҶ’ hard core, soft frontier.

Oracle Classification: Assertions (post-hoc check, catch formatting) vs Rules (prescription, catch reasoning). Conditional oracles may have soft preconditions. Exhaustion handler: escalate, error-value(вҠҘ), partial-accept.

Frontier Growth (вҠўвҠў): Spawner cells create new cells joining the frontier. Semantic automata вҖ” never-terminating. Monotonicity preserved, confluence preserved, termination not guaranteed. В§ marks crystallization boundary.

Cell-as-Agent Pattern: inbox вҶ’ В§handlers[] вҶ’ dispatch вҶ’ results[] вҶ’ act вҶ’ actions[]. Cell's eval/apply. Code-as-data via В§. Open: streaming, error propagation."

  вҠў= word-count вҶҗ 347

-- eval-one: document is a hard cell (вҠў=). Deterministic evaluation.
