--   report:                frozen (final summary = 82 words, ratio 0.236)
--
-- Compression achieved: 347 вҶ’ 155 вҶ’ 82 words (76.4% reduction).
-- Level-3 attempt would have required ~41 words, but the retry-inflated
-- level-2 re-summary (88 words) lost too many critical concepts (fidelity 3),
-- triggering guard-induced вҠҘ at compress-further-1 and halting the loop.
--
-- Total frames: 8 (frame 0 through frame 7)
-- Spawner fires: 1 (recurse-compression, iteration 0)
-- Guard-induced вҠҘ: 1 (compress-further-1, check-fidelity-1вҶ’acceptable = false)
-- вҠҘ propagation: compress-further-1 вҶ’ recurse-compression (permanent block)
-- Oracle retries: 3 (summarize-1, file-scope вҠЁ? policy, floor constraint conflict)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- v0.2 OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-guard-as-stop вҶҗ "Guard clauses provide a cleaner mechanism for вҠҘ-as-stop-signal
than the R16 approach of having the LLM explicitly yield вҠҘ. In R16, compress-further
had to decide in its вҲҙ body whether to output вҠҘ. In v0.2, the guard clause on
check-fidelityвҶ’acceptable makes this decision structural: the cell is skipped
automatically when acceptable = false. The LLM is relieved of the responsibility
to produce вҠҘ вҖ” the graph topology handles it. This is both more reliable (no
risk of LLM forgetting to yield вҠҘ) and more compositional (guard logic is visible
to the scheduler without evaluating the cell body)."

вҠў= obs-oracle-bound-drift вҶҗ "The spawned summarize-1 cell inherits oracle bounds
from the original summarize cell (actual-word-count вүҘ 86.75), but its input is
only 82 words. This creates a genuine constraint conflict: the LLM cannot compress
to 50% (41 words) AND stay above the floor. The retry mechanism inflated the
summary from 41 to 88 words вҖ” producing a WORSE summary (fidelity 3) than the
natural 41-word version would have been. This suggests oracle bounds on spawned
chains need to be parameterized relative to the input length, not hard-coded
to the original document. A v0.3 consideration: вҠЁ expressions should reference
the cell's own given values, not literals from the template."

вҠў= obs-given-question-scoping вҶҗ "The report cell uses given? to tolerate вҠҘ from
compress-further, but in this trace compress-further actually produced output.
The вҠҘ propagation occurred one level deeper (compress-further-1). The report
cell's given? never saw вҠҘ вҖ” it saw a real value. This means report correctly
uses the last successfully compressed output. The given? mechanism works best
when the вҠҘ-producing cell is a DIRECT dependency. For multi-level spawned chains,
the вҠҘ propagation at deeper levels is handled by the вҠўвҠў spawner blocking, not
by given?. Two different вҠҘ-tolerance mechanisms for two different scopes."

вҠў= obs-bottom-propagation-chain вҶҗ "The вҠҘ propagation chain in this trace:
  check-fidelity-1вҶ’acceptable = false
  вҶ’ guard on compress-further-1 fails
  вҶ’ compress-further-1 yields вүЎ вҠҘ (guard-induced bottom)
  вҶ’ recurse-compression given compress-further-1вҶ’next-summary blocks on вҠҘ
  вҶ’ no further spawner iterations
This is exactly the v0.2 'guard-induced bottom' mechanism (spec section:
Bottom Propagation, rule 3). The chain terminates cleanly without any cell
needing to 'know' it should stop. The graph structure encodes the stopping
logic. This validates v0.2's claim that вҠҘ propagation is the natural
termination mechanism for recursive spawner patterns."

вҠў= obs-retry-vs-guard-interaction вҶҗ "An interesting design tension: summarize-1
hit oracle bounds and retried 3 times (inflating from 41 to 88 words), while
compress-further-1 was guard-blocked (yielding вҠҘ) because fidelity was too low.
The retries CAUSED the low fidelity вҖ” padding a summary to meet an artificial
floor destroys compression quality. Without the oracle bound conflict, the
natural 41-word summary might have scored fidelity 5-6 (acceptable), and the
loop would have continued. The вҠЁ? retry mechanism and the guard-induced вҠҘ
mechanism interacted adversarially here. In production Cell, this would be
a signal to refine the oracle bounds, not the retry policy."
